s=Step.new(recipe_id: 331, step: "Step 1 preheat oven to 350 Step 2 Brown ground beef in skillet over medium/ med. high heat adding taco seasoning as it cooks. Drain off grease. Pour drained beef into a deep 13x 9 inch casserole dish. Step 3 In large bowl combine all other ingredients. Step 4 Pour mixture into the casserole dish over the beef and bake for about 45 minutes or until edges are brown.")
