s=Step.new(recipe_id: 355, step: "Step 1 Preheat your oven to 350 degrees. Step 2 But your stick of butter in a 9x13 casserole dish and put it in the oven until the butter is mostly melted. While you are melting the butter open & drain your whole kernel corn. Step 3 Remove 9x13 dish add all of your ingredients and stir with a spoon until everything is mixed together. (Be careful the dish is hot!) Step 4 Bake for 30 - 40 minutes. ENJOY!")
