s=Step.new(recipe_id: 470, step: "Directions: Preheat oven to 350. Grease a muffin tin with butter and set aside. Remove crust from bread slices and cut into squares or rectangles slightly larger than muffin cavities. Place slices in muffin tin pressing down so the bread comes up the sides. Sprinkle evenly with bacon. In a bowl whisk eggs half and half mustard salt and pepper until combined. Stir in half the cheese. Pour over bread and bacon and top with remaining cheese. Bake for 15-20 minutes until egg is set. Garnish with chopped chives. Makes 12-15 mini strata")
