s=Step.new(recipe_id: 494, step: "In a large soup pot heat the olive oil over medium heat. Add in the onion and garlic and cook for 1 minute. Add in the carrots celery and cumin and cook for 5-7 minutes or until vegetables are softened. Pour in the chicken stock  base canned tomatoes and V-8 salt and pepper. Cook for 15 minutes. Toss in the zucchini and squash and cook 5 more minutes. Serve with salsa fresca avocado and chips")
