s=Step.new(recipe_id: 624, step: "boil 4 boneless skinless chicken breasts in a large soup pot for 20 minutes with seasonings to your taste. Once done remove from pot and place on a plate to cool. Keep all liquid and turn burner down to medium heat. Peel and dice 4 medium sized baking potatos. Dice one whole small onion whichever color you prefer. Peel and dice one WHOLE bulb of garlic and two peeled large carrots or 10 small baby carrots. Place all diced vegetables in chicken stock and cook for 45 minutes. After 45 minutes cube chicken and place in chicken stock. add 1 1/2 cups of white or brown rice. Cook for an additional 25-30 minutes. add 1 12 oz can of drained sweet peas. Season to taste. ( I usually add rosemary italian seasonings garlic salt and pepper)")
