s=Step.new(recipe_id: 633, step: "Stuffed Squash with Rice and Meat After washing the squash cut the two ends off then with a tubal squash meat remover take out the meat of the squash. In a large bowl add meat riceonion parsley 1/2 tsp salt 1/8 tsp pepper juice of half lemon 2 TBSP oil and mix well. Stuff each squash with mixture. In a skillet add 2 TBSP oil and fry squash lightly and transfer to a casserole. Add other half lemon 2 cups water salt & pepper to taste and let simmer on a low heat for 1 hour. Check if meat is cooked. If not let remain on low heat until cooked and enjoy when done.")
