s=Step.new(recipe_id: 646, step: "Step 1 Put the tomatoes basil and Sherry in a large Dutch oven set over medium heat with half of the onion garlic and lemon juice. Cook for 2-3 minutes just until onions are softened and garlic is fragrant. Add the mussels and cover. Cook 10 minutes or until mussels have all opened. Step 2 While the mussels are cooking add all the remaining ingredients except the parsley to a saucepan and reduce by half. Step 3 Pour the sauce over the mussels stir the pot top with the chopped parsley and serve with a loaf of crusty bread.")
